				<p style="color: #3f3f3f; font-size: 14px; font-family: poppins; margin-top: 5px;">
				
				<b style="color:#0d6b9c;">Introduction</b><br><br>
				Jira Software is used for Issue tracking and project management, providing effective and efficient software delivery. The engineers working on ServiceNow Incident may need to create a Task in Jira Issue for the engineering team to work on this.<br><br>
				</p>
								
				<p style="color: #3f3f3f; font-size: 14px; font-family: poppins; margin-top: 5px;">
				<b style="color:#0d6b9c;">Impact on the Business:</b><br>
				
				<ul style="color: #3f3f3f; font-size: 14px; font-family: poppins; margin-top: 10px;">
					<li>Improper Management of Information</li>
					<li>Errors Caused due to Duplication of Updates in Multiple Applications</li>
					<li>The Effort needed to update, manage and track activities in different instances</li>
					<li>The Effort involved results in Time and Manpower, which indirectly contributes to the Operational Cost</li>
				
				</ul>
								
				
				</p>
				
